\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
\Phi_{1}\\
\Phi_{2}\\
\Phi_{3}
\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\Phi_{3}\\
\Phi_{2}\\
-\Phi_{1}
\end{array}\right)\\
