\begin_layout Standard
QCD中的对称性是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
G=SU(N)\times SU(N)=\left\{ (L,R)|L\in SU(N),R\in SU(N)\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

and
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
H=\left\{ (V,V)\right\} |V\in SU(N)\cong SU(N)
\]

\end_inset

如果
\begin_inset Formula $N=2$
\end_inset

 for massless 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 quarks and 
\begin_inset Formula $N=3$
\end_inset

 for massless u, d and s quarks.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
令
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{g}=(\tilde{L},\tilde{R})\in G$
\end_inset

，我们用用
\begin_inset Formula $SU(N)$
\end_inset

矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $U=\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

刻画陪集元素，如此可写成：
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{g}H=(1,\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger})H$
\end_inset

。这是一种约定，我们令陪集的代表元素的首位上是单位矩阵（相当于一起从右边乘上
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{L}^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

）。
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $g=(L,R)\in G$
\end_inset

下的变换行为，同构于左陪集
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{g}H$
\end_inset

左乘
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g\tilde{g}H=(L,R\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger})H=(1,R\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger}\tilde{L}^{\dagger})(L,L)H=(1,R(\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger})L^{\dagger})H
\]

\end_inset

这里我们使用了群的重排定理。任何元素
\begin_inset Formula $\left(L,L\right)\in H$
\end_inset

乘以
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

得到
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

自己。根据我们的约定，变换后的陪集的代表元素是
\begin_inset Formula $\left(1,R\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger}L^{\dagger}\right)$
\end_inset

。因此,
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

的变换行为是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U=\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger}\mapsto U^{\prime}=R(\tilde{R}\tilde{L}^{\dagger})L^{\dagger}=RUL^{\dagger}
\]

\end_inset

如果乘上的是子群
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

的群元
\begin_inset Formula $(V,V)$
\end_inset

，按照之前的约定，等价于乘上的是
\begin_inset Formula $(1,VV^{\dagger})=(1,1)$
\end_inset

，所以陪集代表元
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

子群的变换具有不变性。到这里，
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

是某些幺正矩阵，跟
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

的商群是同态关系。但
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

不一定对应物理上的场。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在我们定义三个空间：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{1}\equiv\begin{cases}
\left\{ \Phi:M^{4}\to\mathbb{R}^{3}|\phi_{i}:M^{4}\to\mathbb{R}\text{ smooth}\right\}  & \text{for }N=2\\
\left\{ \Phi:M^{4}\to\mathbb{R}^{8}|\phi_{i}:M^{4}\to\mathbb{R}\text{ smooth}\right\}  & \text{for }N=3
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{2}\equiv\left\{ \phi:M^{4}\to\tilde{\mathscr{H}}(N)|\phi\text{ smooth}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{\mathscr{H}}(N)\equiv\left\{ A\in\text{gl}\left(N,\mathbb{C}\right)|A^{\dagger}=A\land\tr(A)=0\right\} $
\end_inset

, 所有的
\begin_inset Formula $N\times N$
\end_inset

无迹厄米矩阵。他们在矩阵加法下组成一个实矢量线性空间。
\begin_inset Formula $S_{2}$
\end_inset

映射是 Minkowski 
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset

–维空间到一个无迹矩阵的映射，每一个entry 是一个光滑函数。对于
\begin_inset Formula $N=2$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $S_{1}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{2}$
\end_inset

 可以像下面这样联系起来：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\phi=\sum_{i=1}^{3}\phi_{i}\tau_{i}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\phi_{3} & \phi_{1}-i\phi_{2}\\
\phi_{1}+i\phi_{2} & -\phi_{3}
\end{array}\right)\equiv\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\pi^{0} & \sqrt{2}\pi^{+}\\
\sqrt{2}\pi^{-} & -\pi^{0}
\end{array}\right)\label{eq:3.36}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\tau_{i}$
\end_inset

是通常的 Pauli 矩阵 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{i}=\frac{1}{2}\tr\left[\tau_{i}\phi\right]$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula $N=3$
\end_inset

是类似的，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\phi=\sum_{a=1}^{8}\phi_{a}\lambda_{a}\equiv\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
\pi^{0}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\eta & \sqrt{2}\pi^{-} & \sqrt{2}K^{+}\\
\sqrt{2}\pi^{+} & -\pi^{0}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\eta & \sqrt{2}K^{0}\\
\sqrt{2}K^{-} & \sqrt{2}\bar{K}^{0} & \frac{-2}{\sqrt{3}}\eta
\end{array}\right)\label{eq:3.37}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

例如有
\begin_inset Formula $\pi^{+}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(\phi_{1}-i\phi_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
最后定义一个
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{3}\equiv\left\{ U:M^{4}\to SU(N)|U=\exp\left(i\frac{\phi}{F_{0}}\right),\phi\in M_{2}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $F_{0}$
\end_inset

是一个量纲约化因子，和玻色子场量纲一样，为
\begin_inset Formula $E^{1}$
\end_inset

。稍后会确定
\begin_inset Formula $F_{0}$
\end_inset

为手征极限下的衰变常数。这里需要注意的是
\begin_inset Formula $S_{3}$
\end_inset

并不是一个矢量空间，因为两个
\begin_inset Formula $SU(N)$
\end_inset

的和不是
\begin_inset Formula $SU(N)$
\end_inset

矩阵。到这里，我们的
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

才有了物理意义，开始对应物理上的场。我们同时也引入对坐标
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的依赖。
\begin_inset Formula $U(x)=\exp\left(\frac{i\phi(x)}{F_{0}}\right)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
可以在
\begin_inset Formula $S_{3}$
\end_inset

上定义群
\begin_inset Formula $SU(N)\times SU(N)$
\end_inset

的一个实现（realization）:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi:G\times S_{3}\to S_{3}\quad\text{with}\quad\varphi\left[(L,R),U\right]\equiv RUL^{\dagger}
\]

\end_inset

defines an operation of 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{3}$
\end_inset

，由于
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $RUL^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

是一个
\begin_inset Formula $SU(N)$
\end_inset

矩阵。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\left[\left(1,1\right),U\right]=1U1=U$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
let 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{i}=(L_{i},R_{i})\in G$
\end_inset

and thus 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{1}g_{2}=(L_{1}L_{2},R_{1}R_{2})\in G$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\varphi\left[g_{1},\varphi\left[g_{2},U\right]\right] & =\varphi\left[g_{1},\left(R_{2}UL_{2}^{\dagger}\right)\right]=R_{1}R_{2}UL_{2}^{\dagger}L_{1}^{\dagger}\\
\varphi\left[g_{1}g_{2},U\right] & =R_{1}R_{2}U\left(L_{1}L_{2}\right)^{\dagger}=R_{1}R_{2}UL_{2}^{\dagger}L_{1}^{\dagger}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

映射
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

 is homogeneous of degree one 但是不是一个表示，因为
\begin_inset Formula $M_{3}$
\end_inset

不是一个线性空间。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\phi=0$
\end_inset

(for all 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

), i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $U_{0}=1$
\end_inset

，表示系统的基态。在子群
\begin_inset Formula $H=\left\{ \left(V,V\right)|V\in SU(N)\right\} $
\end_inset

的变化下是不变的（对应QCD中的左手夸克场和右手夸克场按相同的
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

转动），
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi\left[g=(V,V),U_{0}\right]=VU_{0}V^{\dagger}=VV^{\dagger}=1=U_{0}
\]

\end_inset

另一方面，在 `axial transformation' 下，亦即用
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

转动左手夸克场，用
\begin_inset Formula $A^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

转动右手夸克场，基态不会保持不变
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi\left[g=\left(A,A^{\dagger}\right),U_{0}\right]=A^{\dagger}U_{0}A^{\dagger}=A^{\dagger}A^{\dagger}\neq U_{0}
\]

\end_inset

这跟假设的对称性自发破缺一致。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
EQ
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.36"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 中包含了 Goldstone bosons fields。我们想讨论它们在子群
\begin_inset Formula $H=\left\{ (V,V)|V\in SU(N)\right\} $
\end_inset

下的变换性质。展开
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
U & =1+i\frac{\phi}{F_{0}}-\frac{\phi^{2}}{2F_{0}^{2}}+\cdots\mapsto V(1+i\frac{\phi}{F_{0}}-\frac{\phi^{2}}{2F_{0}^{2}}+\cdots)V^{\dagger}\nonumber \\
 & 1+i\frac{V\phi V^{\dagger}}{F_{0}}-\frac{V\phi V^{\dagger}V\phi V^{\dagger}}{2F_{0}^{2}}+\cdots\label{eq:3.38}
\end{align}

\end_inset

我们看到，如果限制对称变换只在子群
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

中，映射
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $S_{2}$
\end_inset

上，定义了一个表示(representation),
\begin_inset Formula $S_{2}\ni\phi\mapsto V\phi V^{\dagger}\in M_{2}$
\end_inset

,因为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left(V\phi V^{\dagger}\right)^{\dagger}=V\phi V^{\dagger}, & \tr\left(V\phi V^{\dagger}\right)=\tr\left(\phi\right)=0\\
V_{1}\left(V_{2}\phi V_{2}^{\dagger}\right)V_{1}^{\dagger} & =\left(V_{1}V_{2}\right)\phi\left(V_{1}V_{2}\right)^{\dagger}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
比如
\begin_inset Formula $SU(3)$
\end_inset

情况下，我们选取参数化
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
